{"tid":155300,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"求開解","createTime":"2017-03-14T02:07:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T00:34:26.000Z","uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"588fe86052251ff61e5c2f5996926f873a69cba9","tid":155300,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:07:59.000Z","msg":"哩一個月不停鑽牛角尖 關於男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同佢傾左幾次 反而覺得worsen左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己都梳理左無數次 想搵到個徵結係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但搵到又點 搵唔同朋友開解左十鳩幾次都係無辦法<br />\n有無華生可以一針見血我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n為左費事俾人話我諗多左<br />\n我啱先寫晒成個思考過程出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋佢mon緊我ac 有興趣討論下既人可以留低tlg<br />\n<br />\n主要目的係想有人可以反駁到我啲觀點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同幫到我自我排解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果佢唔上連登我都想po出黎 我知好多巴絲都面對緊哩個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我真係好撚小器</span>"},{"pid":"73b57be93a6164fe880fe10f0d03162885f4987f","tid":155300,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:44:53.000Z","msg":"嗚毒撚開po無人理"},{"pid":"7a06c4c8cbd01f36c277eb80609ceb64a590136e","tid":155300,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:45:04.000Z","msg":"春春春春春"},{"pid":"8402e9725d5183abc4150bd70d619c42faa27bac","tid":155300,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:52:49.000Z","msg":"挾太山以超北海 語人曰 我不能 是誠不能也<br />\n為寡妻折枝 語人曰 我不能 是不為也 非不能也<br />\n故情之不情 非挾太山以超北海之類也 情之非情 是折枝之類也<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"h